description:
Ben Shapiro, aka the Grim Reaper of the debate world, reveals the three biggest societal problems we face as Americans, including gun control, toxicity on both the right AND left, cancel culture, Gender dysphoria, and climate change... ALSO: humanizing Ben Shapiro - first kiss? Favorite cereal? Favorite podcast? Besides IMPAULSIVE, of course.
